Author-Name: Paul M Vaaler
Author-Workplace-Name: Department of Strategic Management, Carlson School of Management, University of Minnesota, Minneapolis, USA
File-URL: http://www.palgrave-journals.com/jibs/journal/v42/n9/pdf/jibs201136a.pdf
File-Format: Application/pdf
